---
title: Lamb Merguez-Inspired Sausage and Cheese Subs with Fresh Green Salad
description: Our HelloFresh take on this popular Middle Eastern lamb sausage is sure to be a winner, especially in a delicious handheld! Spiced lamb sausages get tucked into soft sub rolls that have been slathered with a cream cheese sauce. Drizzle chili-garlic sauce over top if you want some heat. Dinner tonight pulls out all the stops!
